      <p class="pl-ser"><strong>How can you use Personal Loan?</strong></p>
      <p>Personal loan helps you to meet a wide range of financial requirements that may include medical crises, home improvement or renovation, education, debt consolidation, travel, or wedding</p>
      <p class="pl-ser"><strong>What is the Rate of Interest for Personal Loan?</strong></p>
      <p>Minimum rate of interest 9.5% and maximum 25%</p>
      <p class="pl-ser"><strong>Personal Loan Upper & Lower Limit & Repayment Clause:</strong></p>
      <p>An Individual can apply for personal loan from INR 100,000 to INR 40,00,000 (one lac to forty lac) and repayment period for the same can be anywhere between one year and 5 years.</p>
      <p>How quickly can a bank disburse personal Loan?</p>
      <p>Personal loan can take anywhere between one hour and 3 days  to come into your bank account.</p>
