      <p>To get your personal loan approved, you are required to meet the eligibility criteria, which are as follows:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Minimum documents required. Just KYC and income proof.</li>
        <li>You have to be a residing citizen of India.</li>
        <li>Between 23 and 55 years of age.</li>
        <li>Employed with a corporate, public, MNC, or private company.</li>
        <li>Meet the salary requirement based on your present residence city or town.</li>
        <li>To apply for a loan you should be 21 years old. Maximum age can be up to 60 years for salaried employees. 65 years for self-employed professionals at the time of loan maturity. However, age criteria may vary from institution to institution.</li>
        <li>If all the above criteria match with your banks requirements, you qualify for a loan.</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="pl-ser"><strong>How to Apply for Personal Loan</strong></p>
      <ul>
        <li>Our Financial Assistant will be at your service from start to finish.</li>
        <li>He or she will guide and assist you fill in the online application form with your personal, employment and financial details.</li>
        <li>Help you choose an amount and opt for an appropriate repayment plan to get quick approval</li>
        <li>Our executive will be in touch with the lender bank to keep you posted and get disbursement as early as he can. Many a times we have got approval for clients within 24 hours!</li>
      </ul>
